#: capshipping/templates/about.html:139
msgid "Shipping Process"
msgstr "Processus d’expédition"

#: capshipping/templates/about.html:151
msgid "Request & Booking"
msgstr "Demande et réservation"

#: capshipping/templates/about.html:153
msgid ""
"\n"
"Submit your shipment details and receive a clear quote.\n"
"Our team ensures a smooth and transparent booking process.\n"
msgstr ""
"Soumettez les détails de votre expédition et recevez un devis clair.\n"
"Notre équipe garantit un processus de réservation fluide et transparent.\n"

#: capshipping/templates/about.html:167
msgid "Processing & Shipping"
msgstr "Traitement et expédition"

#: capshipping/templates/about.html:169
msgid ""
"\n"
"We carefully handle, pack, and ship your cargo using reliable\n"
"sea and air freight solutions with real-time updates.\n"
msgstr ""
"Nous manipulons, emballons et expédions soigneusement vos marchandises grâce "
"à des solutions fiables de fret maritime et aérien avec des mises à jour en "
"temps réel.\n"

#: capshipping/templates/about.html:183
msgid "Delivery & Confirmation"
msgstr "Livraison et confirmation"

#: capshipping/templates/about.html:185
msgid ""
"\n"
"Your shipment is delivered safely to its destination,\n"
"with confirmation and full customer satisfaction.\n"
msgstr ""
"Votre expédition est livrée en toute sécurité à destination, avec "
"confirmation et entière satisfaction du client.\n"

