#: capshipping/templates/index.html:133
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"        Shop from your favorite stores in the United States and send your "
"packages directly to our warehouse. We receive, process, and securely "
"deliver your shipments to Haiti and the Dominican Republic with reliable air "
"and sea cargo services. Enjoy fast delivery times, package tracking, secure "
"handling, and a smooth shipping experience from pickup to final "
"destination.\n"
"\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"m gen kek text map tradwi la nan sit mwen ann ann tradwi an frase bon "
"natirel la m pap menm pale wap konn sa pou w fe : Shop from your favorite "
"stores in the United States and send your packages directly to our "
"warehouse...\n"
"\n"
"Achetez dans vos magasins préférés aux États-Unis et envoyez vos colis "
"directement à notre entrepôt...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"        Shop from your favorite stores in the United States and send your "
"packages directly to our warehouse. We receive, process, and securely "
"deliver your shipments to Haiti and the Dominican Republic with reliable air "
"and sea cargo services. Enjoy fast delivery times, package tracking, secure "
"handling, and a smooth shipping experience from pickup to final "
"destination.\n"
"\n"
"Faites vos achats dans vos magasins préférés aux États-Unis et envoyez vos "
"colis directement à notre entrepôt. Nous recevons, traitons et livrons vos "
"expéditions en toute sécurité vers Haïti et la République Dominicaine grâce "
"à nos services fiables de fret aérien et maritime. Profitez de délais de "
"livraison rapides, du suivi de colis, d’une manipulation sécurisée et d’une "
"expérience d’expédition fluide, de la collecte jusqu’à la destination finale."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:143 capshipping/templates/index.html:184
#: capshipping/templates/index.html:226
msgid "Read More"
msgstr "Lire plus"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:157
msgid "Transport Packages"
msgstr "Transport de colis"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:166
msgid ""
"We provide reliable package transportation through both air freight and sea "
"cargo services, giving you flexible and affordable shipping options..."
msgstr ""
"Nous assurons le transport fiable de vos colis par fret aérien et maritime, "
"en vous offrant des options d’expédition flexibles et abordables..."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:173
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"        We provide reliable package transportation through both air freight "
"and sea cargo services, giving you flexible and affordable shipping options "
"based on your needs. Whether you need fast air delivery or cost-effective "
"ocean freight, we safely transport your packages from the USA to Haiti and "
"the Dominican Republic with professional handling and real-time shipment "
"support.\n"
"\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Nous assurons un transport fiable de vos colis grâce à nos services de fret "
"aérien et maritime, en vous offrant des solutions d’expédition flexibles et "
"abordables adaptées à vos besoins. Que vous ayez besoin d’une livraison "
"rapide par avion ou d’un transport maritime économique, nous acheminons vos "
"colis en toute sécurité des États-Unis vers Haïti et la République "
"Dominicaine, avec une prise en charge professionnelle et un suivi des "
"expéditions en temps réel."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:199
msgid "Deliver Packages"
msgstr "Livraison de colis"

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:208
msgid ""
"We ensure your packages are delivered safely and on time to Haiti and the "
"Dominican Republic..."
msgstr ""
"Nous veillons à ce que vos colis soient livrés en toute sécurité et dans les "
"délais en Haïti et en République Dominicaine..."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:215
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"        We ensure your packages are delivered safely and on time to Haiti "
"and the Dominican Republic through our trusted delivery network. From "
"warehouse processing to final delivery, our team handles every shipment with "
"care, providing reliable tracking, secure transportation, and fast customer "
"support to guarantee a smooth delivery experience.\n"
"\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Nous veillons à ce que vos colis soient livrés en toute sécurité et dans les "
"délais en Haïti et en République Dominicaine grâce à notre réseau de "
"livraison fiable. Du traitement en entrepôt jusqu’à la livraison finale, "
