#: capshipping/templates/index.html:387
msgid ""
"Cap Shipping Distribution is dedicated to providing fast, secure, and "
"reliable shipping solutions between the USA, Haiti, and the Dominican "
"Republic. Our mission is to simplify international shipping through trusted "
"customer service, efficient logistics, and affordable delivery options by "
"air and sea."
