"rapides, sécurisées et fiables entre les États-Unis, Haïti et la République "
"Dominicaine. Notre mission est de simplifier le transport international "
"grâce à un service client de confiance, une logistique efficace et des "
"options de livraison abordables par voie aérienne et maritime."

#: capshipping/templates/index.html:394
msgid ""
"Our vision is to become one of the most trusted Caribbean logistics and "
"freight forwarding companies by connecting families and businesses through "
"innovative, secure, and professional shipping services worldwide."
